{
  "stem": "9943.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she had worked-- she, she had-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was a-- some kind of a relative of hers that had this store on Krucha, Krucha in Warsaw-- Krucha, the street, K-R-U-C-H-A.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Had the store of women's clothing and underwear and all that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she used this as a, a living quarter [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because they wanted to have someone sleep in the store so that nobody should steal in the store.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she, she was finished-- she finished seminary to be a teacher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, how would you like to take over my-- this position-- that position to be a night watcher at the store?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she-- I said, well, I, I will be glad to do that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, so she introduced me to those owners.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they liked this idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They liked me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So now-- so I got that-- a big [POINTING] key, like that size, to, to be able to enter that store or come and go-- and could use it to sleep there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because during the daytime they had the, the-- their business going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I liked it there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a living quarter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I gave it the name El Dorado.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, as I say, I had this large key.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in daytime, if I had some time of-- free time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I used to go to the library on [NON-ENGLISH] Street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I like very much that Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got to know very well the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, so I went on studying medicine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the main thing, of course, in the-- during these years was to, to make a living.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Studying was like secondary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was not that the first thing was to study.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
